PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FDrug dealers part of an organised
OL,7,Fcrime group based in Newport that is
OL,8,Festimated to have sold up to five
OL,9,Fmillion pounds worth of drugs have
OL,10,Fbeen jailed for a total of nearly 58
OL,11,Fyears at Cardiff Crown Court.
OL,13,FFour of the men were arrested
OL,14,Fsimultaneously in October 2024, when
OL,15,FGwent Police carried out pre-dawn
OL,16,Fraids around the city.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
