FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FThe arrests were the culmination of a
OL,7,F12 month long investigation by the
OL,8,Fforce, which included surveillance and
OL,9,Fcovert operations. In sentencing Judge
OL,10,FPaul Hobson said that the use of
OL,11,Fchildren - aged 16 and 17 - as drug
OL,12,Frunners in the city was a particularly
OL,13,Fserious factor.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FThe court heard that 37-year-old
OL,7,FZekkam Ali played a leading role. He
OL,8,Fwas in charge of the drug line for
OL,9,Fmost of the year the police were
OL,10,Fmonitoring the group and was the
OL,11,Fprimary contact for the drugs runners
OL,12,Fas well as buying and selling on a
OL,13,Fcommercial scale. He received a
OL,14,Fsentence of 15 years in prison.
OL,16,FOne of the men sentenced on Monday (23
OL,17,FMarch) was 27-year-old Azim Ahmed, who
OL,18,Fwas found with #80,000 in cash found
OL,19,Fin shoe boxes and a safe, as well as a
OL,20,Fquantity of heroin and 700 grams of
OL,21,Fcocaine at his home address.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FThe court heard that Ahmed's role in
OL,7,Fthe organised crime group (OCG) was
OL,8,Fthe cash courier. The prosecution said
OL,9,Fhe had made 316 journeys by taxi over
OL,10,Fthe course of the 12 month operation
OL,11,Fto collect money taken from drug sales
OL,12,Fthat day. Ahmed was sentenced to eight
OL,13,Fyears and eight months in prison for
OL,14,Fthe drug conspiracy charges, and three
OL,15,Fyears for a separate money laundering
OL,16,Fcharge, to be served concurrently.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FThe court heard that the OCG operated
OL,7,Fa drugs line, a phone number where
OL,8,Fcustomers would be told a post code
OL,9,Ffor purchase crack cocaine and heroin
OL,10,Fin Newport, usually on an area of
OL,11,Frough ground. Gwent Police said that
OL,12,Fanalysis of the line found that around
OL,13,F800 numbers interacted with the drugs
OL,14,Fline during the 12 month operation.
OL,15,FThe line did very little advertising,
OL,16,Fsuggesting it had a stable and
OL,17,Festablished customer base.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
