FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FAn expert witness who gave evidence
OL,7,Fduring the court process concluded
OL,8,Fthat the Newport OCG was a
OL,9,F"sophisticated and well run criminal
OL,10,Fenterprise".
OL,12,FThe court previously heard from an
OL,13,Fexpert witness which estimated that
OL,14,Fthe total street value of sold over
OL,15,Fthe course of the drug selling
OL,16,Fconspiracy in the year up until
OL,17,FOctober 2024 could be as much as #5m.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@KO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
