CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FITV Cymru Wales was present at the
OL,7,Farrests of two of the men as part of
OL,8,FGwent Police's Operation Fairfax.
OL,9,FBefore dawn on 24 October 2024,
OL,10,Fofficers used a chainsaw to enter a
OL,11,Fproperty in Newport where they
OL,12,Farrested Mohammed Boota.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FThe court heard that Boota had the
OL,7,Frole of warehouseman and courier for
OL,8,Fthe OCG. Drugs were brought to his
OL,9,Fhome address and then delivered from
OL,10,Fthere to street dealers. Police say he
OL,11,Fwas also present on a trip to meet a
OL,12,Fdrug dealer higher up the chain in
OL,13,FBirmingham. The search of his home
OL,14,Ffound designer trainers and a number
OL,15,Fof phones. He was sentenced to 11
OL,16,Fyears and three months.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FAnother man, Connor Beale, was
OL,7,Fdescribed in court as a customer
OL,8,Ffacing drug dealer. He was witnessed
OL,9,Fby police making hand to hand
OL,10,Fexchanges of drugs and cash, meeting
OL,11,Fcustomers around Newport. While he was
OL,12,Fnot involved in wholesale supply, he
OL,13,Fdid meet with more senior members of
OL,14,Fthe OCG in order to restocked, and to
OL,15,Fhand over cash proceeds to Mr Ahmed.
OL,16,FBeale was given a sentence of 6 years
OL,17,Fin prison.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
