PN,46410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FA search of 33-year-old Asjad Ali's
OL,7,Fhome found a hydraulic press, for use
OL,8,Fin compressing large quantities of
OL,9,Fdrugs to be sold. He was sentenced to
OL,10,F10 years in prison.
OL,12,FHis ex-partner, 32-year-old Sarah
OL,13,FChant, was given a two year prison
OL,14,Fsentence, suspended for two years, for
OL,15,Fher role in assisting Mr Ali in making
OL,16,Fdeliveries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
