CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1774379485
OL,3,CGang who used children as drug runners
OL,4,Csentenced to nearly 60 years
OL,6,FThe court heard that 32-year-old
OL,7,Ffather of three Anthony Caruana had a
OL,8,Fbrief involvement in the organised
OL,9,Fcrime group during the year police
OL,10,Fwere monitoring them, however he did
OL,11,Fbriefly take control of the drugs
OL,12,Fline. He was sentenced to five years
OL,13,Fin prison.
